a new storm of criticism.

00:10.033 --> 00:15.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump's
decision to abandon the
international climate accord
has global corporations,

00:17.033 --> 00:20.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
American cities and world
leaders calling to keep up the
fight against global warming.

00:22.900 --> 00:26.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
