(BREAK)

01:10.233 --> 01:15.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Reaction to
the president's announcement
yesterday that the U.S. will

01:18.933 --> 01:23.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
withdraw from the Paris
climate agreement has been
unusually fierce on both sides.

01:25.366 --> 01:28.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And, today, the White House
stood firmly by his decision.

01:28.533 --> 01:30.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of
the United States: Thank
you very much, everybody.

01:30.933 --> 01:35.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is slightly less
controversial than yesterday,
but yesterday was a big
service to this country,

01:36.533 --> 01:37.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I will tell you.

01:37.700 --> 01:39.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Thank you very much, everybody.

01:39.833 --> 01:44.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
