agreement is very regrettable,
and I'm expressing
myself in a very reserved

02:27.266 --> 02:29.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
way when I say that.

02:29.366 --> 02:33.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We in Germany, in Europe and
in the world are now more
determined than ever to pool

02:33.600 --> 02:36.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
all our strength to face one
of the challenges of humankind.

