03:51.433 --> 03:55.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Disney's chief, Bob Iger,
joined Musk in resigning
from presidential advisory
committees in protest.

03:58.666 --> 04:03.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Peabody Energy,one of
the country's largest
coal companies, did
come out in support of

04:04.533 --> 04:06.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the president's decision.

04:06.533 --> 04:11.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
