Trump actually believes that
humans play a role in climate

04:46.000 --> 04:48.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
change, Pruitt
skirted the question.

04:48.066 --> 04:50.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SCOTT PRUITT: The discussions
the president and I have had
over the last several weeks

04:50.866 --> 04:55.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
