key issue: Is Paris good
or bad for this country?

04:55.400 --> 04:57.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He determined it was
bad for our country.

04:57.633 --> 04:58.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It hurt us economically.

04:58.866 --> 05:00.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It didn't achieve good
environmental outcomes.

05:00.766 --> 05:03.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
