elsewhere in the complex.

06:37.000 --> 06:42.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: We are still investigating
and trying to ascertain why
somebody will be so senseless

06:43.300 --> 06:45.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
and have such a motive.

06:45.266 --> 06:47.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
