since the Cold War.

07:55.800 --> 08:00.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
VLADIMIR PUTIN (through
translator): Therefore,
I think it is necessary
to stop this useless

08:03.200 --> 08:05.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
