21:27.500 --> 21:31.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think it is going to
get better going forward,
but the bottom line
is, that is not really

21:31.333 --> 21:33.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the way to count it.

21:33.300 --> 21:37.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Diane
