22:20.166 --> 22:24.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Buckhannon
is a town with a population
of less than 6,000.

22:24.033 --> 22:28.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's a deeply conservative
place with a long
history tied to coal.

22:28.166 --> 22:31.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
