the men in their lives.

22:40.733 --> 22:45.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Our Elizabeth Flock has
published a deep look
at these divisions and
the women on the front

22:45.033 --> 22:46.500 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
lines.

22:46.500 --> 22:48.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It sounds like a tough
climate to protest Trump.

22:48.733 --> 22:50.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH FLOCK: Absolutely.

22:50.300 --> 22:52.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I think it's very isolating for
a lot of the women in the town.

22:52.433 --> 22:57.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
