other women there
doing the same thing.

24:06.400 --> 24:10.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And, as
you point out, their protests
are met with counterprotests.

24:10.466 --> 24:12.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What is that like?

24:12.500 --> 24:16.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELIZABETH FLOCK: Well, the most
striking example was after the
announcement of the proposed

24:18.733 --> 24:21.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
travel ban, when the
women did a march at
the county courthouse,
and a number of trucks

24:21.166 --> 24:25.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
showed up in counterprotest,
mostly men, members of
the local fraternity
from the nearby college

24:27.733 --> 24:31.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and other locals, and
basically spewed smoke at the
women as they were marching.

24:31.566 --> 24:34.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They were enveloped in a
huge cloud of black smoke,
dropped firecrackers.

24:34.666 --> 24:39.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was a scary scene in which
a lot of the women tried not
to run or scream and give

24:40.833 --> 24:42.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the men the reaction
that they wanted.

24:42.866 --> 24:45.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: What are
the actions that these women
are taking that they hope have

24:45.633 --> 24:47.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
long-term consequences?

24:47.733 --> 24:52.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELIZABETH FLOCK: So, obviously
showing up in the streets with
posters and sort of telling

24:54.100 --> 24:55.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the town of Buckhannon
that we are here and not
everyone agrees with you.

24:55.500 --> 24:57.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They are lobbying
local representatives.

24:57.733 --> 25:02.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
One of the women held a town
hall with the Republican --
for the Republican senator,

25:02.633 --> 25:04.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
who didn't show up.

25:04.133 --> 25:06.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, she held this town hall
anyway to an empty chair.

25:06.833 --> 25:10.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And a lot of them are traveling
to meet with other -- they
are part of the Indivisible

25:10.533 --> 25:13.100 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
group.

25:13.100 --> 25:15.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they're traveling to
meet other Indivisible
groups, which is a liberal
anti-Trump grassroots

25:15.166 --> 25:17.666 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
organization.

25:17.666 --> 25:21.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so they are sort
