26:12.766 --> 26:14.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN:
Plenty to follow up on.

26:14.966 --> 26:19.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Liz Flock, thanks
for joining us.

26:21.166 --> 26:25.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH FLOCK: Thank you.

26:25.300 --> 26:30.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: At the end of
another week jam-packed with
news from Washington, it's

26:31.166 --> 26:33.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
time for Shields and Brooks.

26:33.200 --> 26:36.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
