Mark Shields and New York
Times columnist David Brooks.

26:36.566 --> 26:38.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Welcome, gentleman.

26:38.666 --> 26:43.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, what is there to talk about,
Mark, but yesterday's climate
change decision, the president's

26:45.400 --> 26:49.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
